ORTHOPEDIC COMPLICATIONS IN HIV PATIENTS.

Lima AL(1), Godoy AL(1), Oliveira PR(1), Gobbi RG(1), de Almeida Silva C(1), 
Martino PB(1), Gutierrez EB(2), Gianna MC(3), Camanho GL(1).

Author information:
(1)Institute of Orthopedics and Traumatology (IOT), Hospital das Clínicas, 
School of Medicine, Universidade de Sao Paulo.
(2)HIV/AIDS Patient Care Clinic Extension, Division of Infectious and Parasitic 
