Extrapolating Survival from Randomized Trials Using External Data: A Review of 
Methods.

Jackson C(1), Stevens J(2), Ren S(2), Latimer N(2), Bojke L(3), Manca A(3), 
Sharples L(4).

Author information:
(1)MRC Biostatistics Unit, Cambridge, United Kingdom of Great Britain and 
